column5: On the way back from the Parry Sound area,we saw a place called Musky's,right on the Rt.69,near Honey Harbour.Does anyone know the web site,or phone# there?I'm looking to return to the Bay,of course Musky fishing.I also need a chart for that area.Mine goes to Bying inlet,and Parry Sound.Help guy's, as I know this is the place to find out,what I need to know.Thank you in advance.
